title: Apricot Chicken & Roast Cauliflower Salad with Yoghurt & Toasted Almonds
description: For tonight’s dinner, we’ve enlisted the help of a lively glaze made with apricot sauce, soy sauce and brown sugar: it coats each bite of tender chicken breast in sticky stone-fruit sweetness and even tastes great drizzled over the robust roast veggie salad with fluffy cauliflower. Go for your life!

